channel.title: YouTube.ca Rick Rolled me
channel.description:
I just went to YouTube.ca and I see this video "Earth Hour 2008: TORONTO", interested, I click it only to sadly find out I was just rick rolled by the company that is YouTube. Anyone else fall for it? I would appear that all home page videos lead to Rick Astley.
-Holic
